import React from 'react' const Clubs = () => { return (

Clubs and Focused Groups

Annuity Club

However, due to the short number of courses available at IIT GN and the caps that they have, a lot of people fail to explore this field in detail. IIT Gandhinagar community has many finance enthusiasts, however, we lack a platform that would serve as a promoter of these interests and developing curiosity.
